	<key>readme</key>
	<string>• lect — today's USCCB daily readings
• lect 1d — readings N days from today
• lect sunday — readings for the next Sunday (or today, if today is Sunday)
• lect july 31 — readings for the next July 31
• lect job 8 — Job, chapter 8
• lect 1 kgs 13 — 1 Kings, chapter 13

Book names and SBL abbreviations are case-insensitive.

